  "source_notes": "Sy Scholfield quotes from birth certificate published and transcribed online:  http://www.ilpiccio.it/Mostra/pannello_01.htm\\n\\n\"Carnovale di Montegrino, Mille ottocento quattro addì ventinove settembre: Giò(vanni) Andrea Carnovale Fig(li)o di Giò(vanni) Batt(ist)a, e di Serafina Carnovale Legittimi consorti abitanti in Montegrino è nato quest’oggi circa Le ore dodeci.\"\\n\\nTranslation: \"Carnovale of Montegrino, In the year eighteen hundred and four on the twenty-ninth day in September: To Gio (vanni) Andrea Carnovale son of Gio (vanni) Batt (ist) a, and Serafina Carnovale, legitimate spouses and inhabitants of Montegrino, was born today about twelve hours.\"\\n",
